{
  "info": {
    "name": "ScanPet Mobile Backend API v5",
    "description": "FULL v5 collection. Contains every v4 endpoint plus v5 additions. See docs/API_v5_FRONTEND_CHANGES.md for the change diff. Highlights:\n- Refunds: POST /api/orders/refund (new body shape with items[]); auto Refunded(3)/PartiallyRefunded(4) status.\n- User photo: /api/users/{id}/photo (admin) and /api/auth/me/photo (self).\n- itemImageUrl on every item-bearing response.\n- ?keyword= on every paginated list (matches translations in ALL languages too).\n- Discounts CRUD under /api/discounts (per-row IsStackable + IsRevertable, scope 0/1/2, amount=null when 0).\n- Multilanguage: /api/translations/{entityType}/{entityId}, Accept-Language: en|ar|all.",
